England Moves to Top of World Cricket Rankings After Beating India in Test

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-13T14:09:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-13/england-moves-to-top-of-world-cricket-rankings-after-beating-india-in-test.html
England  defeated  India  by an innings
and 242 runs to guarantee itself the top spot in the cricket
world rankings for the first time.  James Anderson claimed four wickets as India was bowled out
for 244 in the third Test at Edgbaston in Birmingham. England
yesterday declared on 710-7 after Alastair Cook scored a career-
best 294. India was 224 all out in its first innings.  England leads the four-match series 3-0. It needed to win
by at least two Tests to replace India as No. 1 in the
